PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776931533
OL,3,CPM claims civil servant's evidence
OL,4,C'put to bed' allegations against him
OL,6,FKeir Starmer has claimed the evidence
OL,7,Fof former foreign office civil servant
OL,8,FSir Olly Robbins "puts to bed all the
OL,9,Fallegations levelled at me".
OL,11,FSpeaking during PMQs on Wednesday,
OL,12,FStarmer said Robbins had been clear in
OL,13,Fhis testimony to the Foreign Affairs
OL,14,FSelect Committee that he did not feel
OL,15,Funder pressure to waive through Peter
OL,16,FMandelson's security clearance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776931533
OL,3,CPM claims civil servant's evidence
OL,4,C'put to bed' allegations against him
OL,6,F"Sir Olly Robbins could not have been
OL,7,Fclearer in his evidence yesterday,"
OL,8,Fsaid Starmer, referring to the man he
OL,9,Fsacked as Permanent Under-Secretary,
OL,10,Fthe most senior civil service post at
OL,11,Fthe foreign office.
OL,13,FStarmer continued: "He said this, 'I
OL,14,Fdidn't feel under pressure personally
OL,15,Fin terms of my judgments', he went on
OL,16,Fto say 'I have complete confidence
OL,17,Fthat recommendations to me and the
OL,18,Fdiscussions we had and the decision we
OL,19,Fmade were rigorously independent of
OL,20,Fany pressure.'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776931533
OL,3,CPM claims civil servant's evidence
OL,4,C'put to bed' allegations against him
OL,6,F"On top of that, he was asked if any
OL,7,Fconversations led him to believe that
OL,8,FMandelson needed to take up the role
OL,9,Fregardless of vetting outcomes. He
OL,10,Fsaid: 'I can say with certainty it was
OL,11,Fnever put to me in that way.'"
OL,13,FThe prime minister's interpretation of
OL,14,Fevidence appears to contradict parts
OL,15,Fof what Robbins told MPs on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776931533
OL,3,CPM claims civil servant's evidence
OL,4,C'put to bed' allegations against him
OL,6,FIn his evidence, Robbins said No 10
OL,7,Fhad a "dismissive approach" towards
OL,8,Fthe vetting, and that the foreign
OL,9,Foffice found itself under "constant
OL,10,Fchasing" from Downing Street
OL,11,Fofficials, creating "an atmosphere of
OL,12,Fpressure" to get Mandelson's
OL,13,Fappointment as UK ambassador to the US
OL,14,Fover the line.
OL,16,FThe Whitehall veteran was sacked last
OL,17,Fweek for not telling Starmer that
OL,18,FMandelson had failed vetting checks,
OL,19,Fbut was granted security clearance
OL,20,Fanyway, with mitigations put in place.
OL,26,@tD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776931533
OL,3,CPM claims civil servant's evidence
OL,4,C'put to bed' allegations against him
OL,6,FThe PM previously described it as
OL,7,F"staggering" and "unforgivable" that
OL,8,Fhe was kept in the dark about
OL,9,FMandelson's vetting.
OL,11,FStill, Robbins claimed on Tuesday that
OL,12,Fsome in No 10 questioned whether
OL,13,Fvetting was even necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
